---
title: Oven-Baked Chicken, Chorizo & Veggie Risotto with Parmesan & Baby Leaves
description: We believe weeknight dinners should be tasty and on the table without too much fuss. Hence, we present you with our oven baked chorizo risotto. Minimal stirring, loads of comforting veggies and superbly satisfying — what could be better?
